The paper proposes a method for the automatic semantic annotation of Web services, which involves natural language processing and ontology mapping. This falls under the domain of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also deals with the processing of large collections of Web service descriptions, which could be relevant to computer engineering (cs.CE) and databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper involves the use of concept-to-word association, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
